{
  "stem": "17426.4",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "After Krusche has punished me for buying bread, he demoted me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was no longer the camp-- the commando leader.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Someone else was appointed to be the leader and I was to work as hard as anybody.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, he insisted at the [NON-ENGLISH] that the foreman would put me to the worse work in that camp, so that I would [NON-ENGLISH], so that I would expire.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Krusche was the commandant.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "However, the foreman, the head foreman for whom I worked in-- in the office, didn't want to take his-- his order.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he said, as far as the camp is concerned, he can do whatever he wants with you.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But when you're on-site, come here, you work for me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I am not going to take his orders.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You're going to work in the office as you are.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I was sort of like a little slice of salami between two loaves of bread.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They were two people of power vying about what to do with the Jew.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I knew that I am in the middle, then eventually I will pay the price.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So one day when I came back, he said to me, you will be the first one to hang in this camp.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I will see to it that you hang here.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "No sooner did it-- was he proclaiming that, a few days later, I came back and I saw a gallows erected in the camp.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I knew, and I feared, that he is going to fulfill his threat.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so, shortly thereafter, there was a group of 100 that is to leave the camp, to go to a newly established camp nearby, about 20 kilometers away.",
      "word_count": 28
    }
  ],
